    <!-- Application Structure Plan: This SPA is structured with a fixed left-hand navigation sidebar for quick access to main sections. The main content area is divided into thematic sections: a 'Summary' as an introduction, a 'Timeline' to chronologically visualize education and work experience, a 'Skills' section with interactive charts for languages and soft skills and a tag cloud for IT skills, and an 'Interests' section for personal hobbies. This design offers a clear, intuitive, and non-linear exploration path, allowing recruiters to quickly navigate to areas of interest and understand the applicant's profile efficiently. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: Summary -> Goal: Provide overview -> Viz: Text Block -> Interaction: None -> Justification: Standard introductory format. Timeline -> Goal: Show chronological progression -> Viz: Custom HTML/CSS Vertical Timeline -> Interaction: Hover effects for detail visibility -> Justification: Visually engaging and easy to follow career path. Languages (Skills) -> Goal: Quantify proficiency -> Viz: Horizontal Bar Chart (Chart.js) -> Interaction: Tooltips on hover -> Justification: Clear visual comparison of language levels. Soft Skills (Skills) -> Goal: Illustrate balanced skill profile -> Viz: Radar Chart (Chart.js) -> Interaction: Tooltips on hover -> Justification: Effective for showing multi-faceted skill sets. IT Skills (Skills) -> Goal: List technical competencies -> Viz: HTML/CSS Tags/Badges -> Interaction: Simple hover -> Justification: Clean and easily scannable. Interests -> Goal: Showcase personality -> Viz: HTML/CSS Grid of Items -> Interaction: Simple hover -> Justification: Visually appealing and concise. -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
